Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.18,0:00:23.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,通知所有正在听这次通信的魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在埃兰姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,协会正对君主派魔法师实施大规模肃清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.32,0:00:42.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,得知皇帝继位这一消息的魔法师协会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.83,0:00:45.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了与君主对决的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.29,0:00:48.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会已经是君主的敌人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有交涉的余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.92,0:00:52.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必对交会而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.63,0:00:55.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝圣印的威胁就是有这么大吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.43,0:01:02.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这次通信结束后就折断魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.89,0:01:05.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,利用嵌入魔杖的嵌入混沌仪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.85,0:01:08.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就可掌握我们身在何处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以认为通过魔杖进行的通信均被窃听了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.49,0:01:16.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会的暗影比想象中更深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:22.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不  或许那暗影才是教会的本质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.58,0:03:13.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才全体魔法师收到了埃兰姆发生骚乱的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.67,0:03:18.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎被视作君主派的魔法师们正接连遭到肃清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为提欧阁下继位皇帝了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.30,0:03:26.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  于是皇帝圣印的诞生已势在必行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  魔法师协会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎将以皇帝为首的全体君主视为了敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  我们今后该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只能战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,与埃兰姆的魔法师协会战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我将宣布今后的方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  请听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.08,0:03:55.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从此刻起  将条约  联合  同盟三军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,统合为皇帝军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明天中午  为平定骚乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝军将朝埃兰姆进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  魔法师协会是强大的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以预计到  这会是一场困难的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不想参与这场战斗的人大可回国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家在出发前好好想清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,各位魔法师打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已发誓要永远效忠提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟提欧大人一起行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为君主效劳是魔法师的本分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不会有变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能抛弃赛尔杰大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克大人是一位值得让人效忠的君主哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,最主要的是他高度评价我的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德吉雅大人虽然行为自由奔放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过人非常温柔像少女一般纯粹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连背德都能接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能辜负这样一位大人的信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要身为魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那效忠教会就是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.75,0:05:19.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,赫斯奇欧阁下……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.46,0:05:24.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此  我不得不背弃契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  我要回埃兰姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你长久以来为我效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢留下来的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此有一个重要的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.08,0:06:02.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家能折断手上的魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,折断魔杖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不就没法施放魔法了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就很困难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  魔杖拥有一个机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能利用混沌仪向魔法师协会报告持有魔杖的魔法师的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  通过魔杖进行的通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎全部被教会听见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.77,0:06:26.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不能使用魔杖了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就将破坏魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,作为离开魔法师协会的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.43,0:06:54.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合和同盟约有三分之一的君主正在准备回国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的大约有五万人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有三分之一的魔法师回埃兰姆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,战力减弱不可避免啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔杖的销毁贯彻下去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我让剩下的魔法师折断了魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不用担心被魔法师协会窃听了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没魔杖倒是也能使用魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可无法通信就很麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如今  提欧大人已成为皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是皇帝军的魔法师首领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如今比起消沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,更应该思考不用魔杖进行的通信方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.43,0:07:34.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.40,0:07:43.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能跟父亲共事了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  还是父亲的上司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.29,0:08:05.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你要不要也一起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还在记恨那时的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这不废话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪可能忘记他险些杀死西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.41,0:08:40.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  经过那次事件我差点被选别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我在上魔法学校的时候是个问题儿童
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,经常违反规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还在魔兽园放跑了那只猫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把我叫成猫就太失礼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喉咙被挠就这么舒服的家伙还好意思说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然为了这家伙差点死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.03,0:09:15.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在无法忍受殿下像囚犯一样被关在笼子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.62,0:09:23.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那时最支持选别的是魔法学校的校长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而这家伙没有否定校长的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙想保护的不是西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而是规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉也袒护了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.17,0:09:39.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无非是在不知不觉中被被艾雪拉带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我的宝贝妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会袒护你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙当时也该这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都是过去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好好活着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  在处分撤回之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸抱着我大哭了一场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这更让我开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人总是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难以下决定时  就会把道理放在感情之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等事情结束后  才开始犯愁哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是怎么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.30,0:10:23.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言  西露卡和我究竟算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为曾是流浪君主的提欧大人效力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还扶持他成为了皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是魔法师的典范
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.07,0:10:44.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,替不成器的我保护了西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那时以及现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.41,0:10:53.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是我宝贵的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是梅蕾蒂斯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  在明早之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会完成皇帝军的重编方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.44,0:11:18.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲请备齐给诸国的行军指令书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.94,0:11:19.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉就为了明天的行军做准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.58,0:11:29.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,晩安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.77,0:12:01.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我与艾雪拉及父亲一起生活的日子竟然还会到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡  快起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.72,0:12:23.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算杀了西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.74,0:12:51.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还打算把提欧・科尔内罗也杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.87,0:12:52.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新式玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.09,0:13:06.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…是魔法师协会的…特务机关的命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:07.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  你一直都是密探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.68,0:13:18.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡  你早就被特务机关盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.61,0:13:24.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我逐一报告了你做过什么  在谋划什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.74,0:13:25.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.87,0:13:30.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟没命令我杀了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.30,0:13:44.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,骚乱传开就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,特务机关中有一个秘密组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是潘多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.90,0:14:07.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那里给我下达了指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,命令我杀了提欧•科尔内罗和西露卡•梅蕾蒂斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我下手了最后失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点不对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意失败的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还有更好的方式才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我和西露卡都睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得与其刻意失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不如无视命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪能反抗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能看一下我左边的胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法阵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你被刻卡契约了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.58,0:15:02.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错只要违抗组织的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这魔法阵就会让我心跳停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.18,0:15:19.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…命令我杀了你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不跟我说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要说了  这个就会发动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就没法保护你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,解除…解除的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.47,0:15:59.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她还未到丧命之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔内塞的圣杯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.57,0:16:52.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟…做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,简而言之我就是做了该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真正的圣女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要加入圣印教团吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然救了我让我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可邪纹都消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不就没法像以前一样帮助西露卡了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.26,0:17:22.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  或许会以暗杀皇帝未遂的罪名将我处决吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是故意失败的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以连未遂都不算啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.11,0:17:32.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从某种意义上来说  你拼命保护了我和西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我反倒要谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这方面真让人火大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多事想问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经可以说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.54,0:17:52.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下达暗杀指令的是名叫潘多拉的组织  这点已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.67,0:17:57.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟大圣堂的惨剧也有关吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  让黑魔女雅娜召唤恶魔领主的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我所在的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉都是被选别的影魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,和我这种垫底的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.86,0:18:13.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及雅娜那种宣誓效忠的协助者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是控制混沌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,追求的不是极大混沌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做对谁有好处啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  他们似乎不愿让混沌被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会无法使用魔法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,估计也有这个原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.79,0:18:36.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们告诉我  潘多拉是继承了魔法师协会真正的设立理念的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,监视君主 或者说是管理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.76,0:18:46.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们过去应该埋葬有可能当上皇帝的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.77,0:18:52.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会为何要避免混沌被消灭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.77,0:18:56.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要说是因为魔法师协会真正的设立理念  这倒是可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.82,0:19:03.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  我不明白为什么需要这样的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是因为无法使用魔法这个理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还无法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是很充分的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.83,0:19:16.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人害怕自己拥有的力量消失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吸血鬼之王不也一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主和邪纹使也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  潘多拉的协助者并不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.97,0:19:26.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有传令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,三势力的各阵地出现了骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.61,0:19:37.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说有几名君主和邪纹使像疯了一样大闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总之必须行动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有邪纹帮不上大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我会竭尽所能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让你受苦了  抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你保护了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是家人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是为了可爱的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我拼命都愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.81,0:20:18.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得就算是真正的家人也不会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.61,0:20:22.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是因为有血缘关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有血缘关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.37,0:20:31.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此  必须重视家人的联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是仅有两人的家人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉  你是不是把父亲忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经站在我们这边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后随时都能见面了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  是家人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.22,0:20:47.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我去准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我不希望是女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.03,0:21:13.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜担心的事态发生了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是不希望预感应验啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被特务机关用了就抛弃的君主何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太悲哀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.09,0:21:25.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会觉得皇帝圣印这么碍眼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝圣印究竟有怎样的力量呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前先朝着打到魔法师协会努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  要进攻埃兰姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我方的准备还算不上充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也只能上了
